I can't see rangers generating any more aggro than they already do as being a good thing under any circumstances...ever...period...so let it be written so let it be done.  The only positive change I can forsee coming from this ranger change is maybe now that rangers all over the place will be dieing in record numbers Verant will adequately address the Warrior's plea for a more effective method of taunting (or simply a more effective taunt skill) rather than just saying, &quot;fine, 60 warriors can taunt 60+ mobs).  Thx addressing half the problem and ignoring the other half.<br>
<br>
