<br>
I dont think it will make as big a difference as some people seem to think it will.  This is why I'm glad monks got it.  It does significantly raise damage output because its more common than 5%, but it does not raise damage output by enough to particularly unbalance things.<br>
<br>
With Rangers...I'm not so sure.  There does come a point now where if Rangers play their class to its full effect it becomes difficult to hold aggro to other players.  Until now it has been possible for rangers to control their own aggro by switching weapon types/forgoing the use of spells etc in order to hold aggro to a main tank.  Given, there is a very extreme and small point where rangers &quot;break through&quot; the aggro barrier and make it REALLY a pain in the ass to hold aggro on the people who SHOULD have aggro...but I believe we were knocking on the door of that point already and this may or may not put us through it (depending on several things, one of which is what % of the time Verant allows rangers to fire 3xatk).  <br>
<br>
Of course, it stings a little bit as a warrior to have a skill formerly unique to a warrior and a distinct advantage of being a warrior going to a hybrid (not at all that it goes to monks, because, as I've said before, they should have had it all along), but that will pass.<br>
<br>
All in all, as I previously stated, I believe all of these changes have excellent POTENTIAL to be good across the board.  All but the ranger enhancement should be relatively easy for VI to make people happy with.  Should Verant do their usual POS job of planning out how they want rangers to recieve 3xatk and not test things/make sure they wont just piss rangers off....this change has potential to be an overall negative one. <br>
<br>
 That said, we'll probably have to wait till these changes to go<br>
live to REALLY pass judment on them, as at this point how things will happen on live servers is just conjecture based on test....but if these changes were to go live now, at least one of them has about a 70/30 chance of not working like they wanted it to and just pissing rangers off further cuz they'll die a lot. <p><p align = "center">
